<span id="freeTextContainer4836515517637096441">I’m counting this as one book because it’s read both back to back as part of my books I always wanted to read challenge, and I only want it to count as one book. (It’s number four.)<br/><br/>If I’m being honest Tom Sawyer gets four stars and Huckleberry Finn gets three. Maybe I was tired of these boys and their crazy antics and the racism by the time I got through the second one, but Tom Sawyer was more palatable to me.</span>

          </span>
