        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2370852808" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer18150856582578529100">Huckleberry Finn is first introduced to readers in Tom Sawyer. To try to escape his life of parental abuse and poverty, Finn sets off down the Mississippi River with a runaway slave. They encounter a many varied situations. Racist terms are used as they were acceptable when Clemmens wrote the book.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


